  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposed conversion of the garage in to a self-contained flat, by reason of its siting and form, would introduce an incongruous and inappropriate form of development which would fail to respect the  prevailing pattern of development within the surrounding area and which would fail to satisfactorily relate to its surroundings, contrary to the high quality design aspirations of the National Planning Policy Framework (2021), Policy D3(1)(11) of The London Plan (2021), Core Policy CS1.B of the Harrow Core Strategy (2012), Policy DM1 of the Harrow Development Management Policies Plan (2013), and the Adopted Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Design Guide (2010).",
    "Reason : 2 - The proposed conversion of the garage in to a self-contained flat, by reason of its lack of defensible space to the habitable room windows on the front (north) elevation which would result in loss of privacy for the flat, in conjunction with the lack of private amenity space, bin storage and cycle storage, and its harmful impact to the host property in terms of loss of privacy to the rear garden, would give rise to poor living conditions for the potential future occupiers of the proposed self-contained flat, and for the occupiers of the host dwelling. The proposal is therefore contrary to the high quality design aspirations of the National Planning Policy Framework (2021), Policy D3(7) and D6 of The London Plan (2021), Harrow Development Management Policies Plan (2013), Policy DM1, DM27, DM26, and DM45, of the Development Management Plan Local Policies (2013) and the Adopted Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Design Guide (2010)."
  ],
